{"authors":["江涛","Tolggle","Razon Yang"],"categories":["诗词文章","Installation","Language","RDB","Image"],"pages":[{"authors":[{"title":"江涛","url":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/authors/%E6%B1%9F%E6%B6%9B/"}],"categories":[{"title":"诗词文章","url":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/categories/%E8%AF%97%E8%AF%8D%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0/"}],"content":"《太行路》\n唐 白居易\n太行之路能摧车，若比人心是坦途。\n巫峡之水能覆舟，若比人心是安流。\n人心好恶苦不常，好生毛羽恶生疮。\n与君结发未五载，岂期牛女为参商。\n古称色衰相弃背，当时美人犹怨悔。\n何况如今鸾镜中，妾颜未改君心改。\n为君熏衣裳，君闻兰麝不馨香。\n为君盛容饰，君看金翠无颜色。\n行路难，难重陈。\n人生莫作妇人身，百年苦乐由他人。\n行路难，难于山，险于水。\n不独人间夫与妻，近代君臣亦如此。\n君不见左纳言，右纳史，朝承恩，暮赐死。\n行路难，不在水，不在山，只在人情反覆间。\n","date":"August 25, 2022","img":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/chat/tai-hang-lu/featured-sample.webp","lang":"zh-cn","langName":"简体中文","largeImg":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/chat/tai-hang-lu/featured-sample_hub21423bb251c1b2b7fd14e96b364048a_45218_500x0_resize_q75_h2_box_2.webp","permalink":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/chat/tai-hang-lu/","series":[{"title":"Chat","url":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/series/chat/"}],"smallImg":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/chat/tai-hang-lu/featured-sample_hub21423bb251c1b2b7fd14e96b364048a_45218_180x0_resize_q75_h2_box_2.webp","tags":[{"title":"白居易","url":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/tags/%E7%99%BD%E5%B1%85%E6%98%93/"}],"title":"太行路"},{"authors":[{"title":"江涛","url":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/authors/%E6%B1%9F%E6%B6%9B/"}],"categories":[{"title":"诗词文章","url":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/categories/%E8%AF%97%E8%AF%8D%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0/"}],"content":"儿童版《红楼梦》共11册。一正在上幼儿园大班的小朋友特别喜欢《红楼梦》，她认为《红楼梦》中的故事比 《伊索寓言》等故事更有意思，《红楼梦》中的故事连续性好、故事中的俊男靓女栩栩如生。她央求我给她讲了一遍又一遍，每遍我都尽量结合不同的现实社会场景去引导她认识真实的社会，希望她能从中学会适应社会，将来少走弯路错路。如今讲第三遍了，再次欣赏黛玉葬花片段，由衷叹服曹雪芹先生的文采，诗词拈手就来，不仅文字漂亮，而且真挚、情感饱满。\n《葬花吟》\n花谢花飞花满天，红消香断有谁怜?\n游丝软系飘春榭，落絮轻沾扑绣帘。\n闺中女儿惜春暮，愁绪满怀无释处；\n手把花锄出绣帘，忍踏落花来复去？\n柳丝榆英自芳菲，不管桃飘与李飞；\n桃李明年能再发，明年闺中知有谁？\n三月香巢已垒成，梁间燕子太无情！\n明年花发虽可啄，却不道人去梁空巢也倾。\n一年三百六十日，风刀霜剑严相逼；\n明媚鲜妍能几时，一朝飘泊难寻觅。\n花开易见落难寻，阶前闷杀葬花人；\n独把花锄泪暗洒，洒上空枝见血痕。\n杜鹃无语正黄昏，荷锄归去掩重门；\n青灯照壁人初睡，冷雨敲窗被未温。\n怪奴底事倍伤神？半为怜春半恼春。\n怜春忽至恼忽去，至又无言去不闻。\n昨宵庭外悲歌发，知是花魂与鸟魂？\n花魂鸟魂总难留，鸟自无言花自羞；\n愿奴胁下生双翼，随花飞到天尽头。\n天尽头，何处有香丘？\n未若锦囊收艳骨，一抔净土掩风流；\n质本洁来还洁去，强于污淖陷渠沟。\n尔今死去侬收葬，未卜侬身何日丧？\n侬今葬花人笑痴，他年葬侬知是谁？\n试看春残花渐落，便是红颜老死时。\n一朝春尽红颜老，花落人亡两不知！\n","date":"August 24, 2022","img":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/chat/dai-yu-zang-hua/featured-sample.webp","lang":"zh-cn","langName":"简体中文","largeImg":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/chat/dai-yu-zang-hua/featured-sample_hu88eba0c770952f1305d46492e47f570a_209010_500x0_resize_q75_h2_box_2.webp","permalink":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/chat/dai-yu-zang-hua/","series":[{"title":"Chat","url":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/series/chat/"}],"smallImg":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/chat/dai-yu-zang-hua/featured-sample_hu88eba0c770952f1305d46492e47f570a_209010_180x0_resize_q75_h2_box_2.webp","tags":[{"title":"红楼梦","url":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/tags/%E7%BA%A2%E6%A5%BC%E6%A2%A6/"}],"title":"黛玉葬花"},{"authors":[],"categories":[{"title":"Installation","url":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/categories/installation/"}],"content":"This guide show you how to install on Arch Linux.\n","date":"August 23, 2022","img":"","lang":"zh-cn","langName":"简体中文","largeImg":"","permalink":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/docs/dart/base-type/","series":[{"title":"Guide","url":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/series/guide/"}],"smallImg":"","tags":[{"title":"Mobile","url":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/tags/mobile/"},{"title":"Dart","url":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/tags/dart/"}],"title":"Dart 变量"},{"authors":[],"categories":[{"title":"Language","url":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/categories/language/"}],"content":"Dart语言含有如下 63 个关键字，Go语言25个关键字，关键字个数比Go多很多，从关键字的数量方面讲，在语言语法层面的学习难度比Go要大些。 行号 关键字 关键字 关键字 关键字 1 abstract else import show 2 as enum in static 3 assert export interface super 4 async extends is switch 5 await extension late sync 6 break external library this 7 case factory mixin throw 8 catch false new true 9 class final null try 10 const finally on typedef 11 continue for operator var 12 covariant Function part void 13 default get required while 14 deferred hide rethrow with 15 do if return yield 16 dynamic implements set ","date":"August 22, 2022","img":"","lang":"zh-cn","langName":"简体中文","largeImg":"","permalink":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/docs/dart/key-word/","series":[{"title":"Technology","url":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/series/technology/"}],"smallImg":"","tags":[{"title":"Dart","url":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/tags/dart/"},{"title":"Syntax","url":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/tags/syntax/"}],"title":"Dart 关键字"},{"authors":[{"title":"江涛","url":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/authors/%E6%B1%9F%E6%B6%9B/"}],"categories":[],"content":" 一女士对儿童说：“我在用内功给你疗伤”。 儿童回应：“我没听懂”。 哈哈，“内功”这种“鬼话”，恐怕只有稍有点年龄的中国人才能理解吧。\n","date":"July 25, 2022","img":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/chat/nei-gong/featured-sample.webp","lang":"zh-cn","langName":"简体中文","largeImg":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/chat/nei-gong/featured-sample_hu8387c86bbcf0ac6eae5bfc650783c812_5128_500x0_resize_q75_h2_box_2.webp","permalink":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/chat/nei-gong/","series":[{"title":"Chat","url":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/series/chat/"}],"smallImg":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/chat/nei-gong/featured-sample_hu8387c86bbcf0ac6eae5bfc650783c812_5128_180x0_resize_q75_h2_box_2.webp","tags":[{"title":"文化","url":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/tags/%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96/"}],"title":"内功疗伤"},{"authors":[{"title":"Tolggle","url":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/en/authors/tolggle/"}],"categories":[{"title":"RDB","url":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/en/categories/rdb/"}],"content":"One day, I heard from an architect that Oracle\u0026rsquo;s Sequence may not be incremented, but a random number. This point of view is a bit diffent from my subconscious. I plan to take some time to investigate the implementation principle of Oracle‘s Sequence and summarize an article to improve myself.\n","date":"July 23, 2022","img":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/en/chat/oracle-sequence/featured-sample.webp","lang":"en","langName":"English","largeImg":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/en/chat/oracle-sequence/featured-sample_hu6b8ba536a69f5c8133f482d6899d7a45_34918_500x0_resize_q75_h2_box_2.webp","permalink":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/en/chat/oracle-sequence/","series":[{"title":"Chat","url":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/en/series/chat/"}],"smallImg":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/en/chat/oracle-sequence/featured-sample_hu6b8ba536a69f5c8133f482d6899d7a45_34918_180x0_resize_q75_h2_box_2.webp","tags":[{"title":"Oracle","url":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/en/tags/oracle/"},{"title":"Developer","url":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/en/tags/developer/"}],"title":"Oracle's Sequence"},{"authors":[{"title":"江涛","url":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/authors/%E6%B1%9F%E6%B6%9B/"}],"categories":[{"title":"Image","url":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/categories/image/"}],"content":"某日，听某架构师说 Oracle的Sequence 可能不是递增，而是随机出来的数。这个观点与我潜意识有点不同，回头调研一下Oracle的Sequenc的实现原理，总结一片文章，以提高自己。\n","date":"July 23, 2022","img":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/chat/oracle-sequence/featured-sample.webp","lang":"zh-cn","langName":"简体中文","largeImg":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/chat/oracle-sequence/featured-sample_hu6b8ba536a69f5c8133f482d6899d7a45_34918_500x0_resize_q75_h2_box_2.webp","permalink":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/chat/oracle-sequence/","series":[{"title":"Chat","url":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/series/chat/"}],"smallImg":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/chat/oracle-sequence/featured-sample_hu6b8ba536a69f5c8133f482d6899d7a45_34918_180x0_resize_q75_h2_box_2.webp","tags":[{"title":"DB","url":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/tags/db/"},{"title":"Developer","url":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/tags/developer/"}],"title":"Oracle的sequence"},{"authors":[{"title":"Razon Yang","url":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/authors/razonyang/"}],"categories":[{"title":"Image","url":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/categories/image/"}],"content":"自从 v1.0.0-alpha.1 版本后，便支持了更多的图像处理方法。比如裁剪，适应和填充图像。你也可以在图像上应用滤镜技术。\n技术文档在这里 图像处理.\n","date":"July 8, 2022","img":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/chat/more-image-processing-methods/featured-sample.webp","lang":"zh-cn","langName":"简体中文","largeImg":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/chat/more-image-processing-methods/featured-sample_huc6bcc14d597e300fd9ab4aae536c68a5_498412_500x0_resize_q75_h2_box_2.webp","permalink":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/chat/more-image-processing-methods/","series":[{"title":"News","url":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/series/news/"}],"smallImg":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/chat/more-image-processing-methods/featured-sample_huc6bcc14d597e300fd9ab4aae536c68a5_498412_180x0_resize_q75_h2_box_2.webp","tags":[{"title":"Crop","url":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/tags/crop/"},{"title":"Fit","url":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/tags/fit/"},{"title":"Fill","url":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/tags/fill/"},{"title":"Filters","url":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/tags/filters/"}],"title":"更多的图像处理方法"},{"authors":[],"categories":[],"content":"See also README.md.\n","date":"April 17, 2022","img":"","lang":"zh-cn","langName":"简体中文","largeImg":"","permalink":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/blog/readme/","series":[],"smallImg":"","tags":[{"title":"README","url":"https://blog.zhsit.cn/tags/readme/"}],"title":"README"},{"authors":[],"categories":[],"content":"Written in Go, Hugo is an open source static site generator available under the Apache Licence 2.0. Hugo supports TOML, YAML and JSON data file types, Markdown and HTML content files and uses shortcodes to add rich content. Other notable features are taxonomies, multilingual mode, image processing, custom output formats, HTML/CSS/JS minification and support for Sass SCSS workflows.\nHugo makes use of a variety of open source projects including:\nhttps://github.com/yuin/goldmark https://github.com/alecthomas/chroma https://github.com/muesli/smartcrop https://github.com/spf13/cobra https://github.com/spf13/viper Hugo is ideal for blogs, corporate websites, creative portfolios, online magazines, single page applications or even a website with thousands of pages.\nHugo is for people who want to hand code their own website without worrying about setting up complicated runtimes, dependencies and databases.\nWebsites built with Hugo are extremely fast, secure and can be deployed anywhere including, AWS, GitHub Pages, Heroku, Netlify and any other hosting provider.\nLearn more and contribute on GitHub.\n","date":"February 28, 2019","img":"","lang":"zh-cn","langName":"简体中文","largeImg":"",